<h1>Introduction</h1>

<p>The Bone Necromancer is a classic build that can take on a large variety of content due to its main Damage type being Magic. It is also extremely safe running @@@D2BoneArmor@@@ and having @@@D2BonePrison@@@ available when getting overrun. Definitely a top tier build that does not require a lot of expensive gear to be effective.</p>

<h1>Quick Reference</h1>

<h2>Skill Build</h2>

<p>The following section shows the core skills for the Bone Necromancer. For a detailed breakdown of all core and optional skills as well as the recommended order for allocating skill points, refer to the Skills section of this guide.</p>

<ol>
<li>1 point to all prerequisites</li>
<li>20 points to @@@D2BoneSpirit@@@ - Main single target Damage dealer, required</li>
<li>20 points to @@@D2BoneSpear@@@ - Main Damage dealer, required</li>
<li>20 points to @@@D2BonePrison@@@ - Synergy and useful for Crowd Control, required</li>
<li>20 points to @@@D2BoneWall@@@ - Synergy, required</li>
<li>1+ points to @@@D2CorpseExplosion@@@ - Great for clearing mobs, required</li>
<li>20 points to @@@D2Teeth@@@ - Synergy, required</li>
<li>1 points to @@@D2BoneArmor@@@ - -Prerequisite for @@@D2BoneWall@@@ and also useful for physical Damage absorption, required</li>
<li>1 points to @@@D2AmplifyDamage@@@ - Useful for increasing @@@D2CorpseExplosion@@@ Damage, requjired</li>
</ol>

